* Assigns gun times to the 5k Race
*   When to use:    Just once at the starting gun.
*   How to use:     Update the race name (if different from "5k") and set your specific gun time.
*   Alternative:    Feel free to use the GunTime Prompt to set this up using a handy dialog box!


setgunstart.rsm 5k 09:02:11.15
